name: Unidentified_Twi%27lek_female_dancer
content:
A dancer was a female Twi'lek and an entertainer at the Dealer's Den on the planet Coruscant in 3954 BBY. She was giving a private performance to the Mandalorian mercenary Canderous Ordo when the Mandalorian's friend, legendary Jedi Master Revan, arrived to meet him and discuss what had caused the Mandalorian Wars. After seeing Revan, Ordo dismissed the dancer who stomped off with her head-tails twitching in irritation shooting Revan an angry glare.
This Twi'lek dancer first appeared within Drew Karpyshyn's novel The Old Republic: Revan, which was released in 2011.
